        Form 6 Authority in Queensland: What Sellers Need to Know Before Signing
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A Form 6 is more than a formality. It gives your agent legal authority to act on your behalf. Here is what that authority covers and what to understand before you hand it over.
      </p>
